          After a pleasant, boozy lunch, we returned back to our hotel and continued our laundry chores.

          ---

          That evening, we set off again in search of dinner.

          It was particularly rainy so we tried to find a place in haste. We passed a rather humourously decoared, lurid green weed “dispensary”.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: 'All I managed with my potato-quality iPhone in the rain. I guess you can at least see the colour...', photo: '03/IMG_3257 '})


