          We ended up finding another pub for dinner.

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_restaurant", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '03/streets-of-london', title: 'Streets of London Pub', address: '1501 E Colfax Ave, Denver, CO 80218, USA', price: '$', menu: 'Bar', rating: 3, link: '' })

